Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:03.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この家に　私は一人で住んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:24.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　私には見えない何かが　ここにはいる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:35.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この頃は　あまり怖くなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:42.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,多分　神様みたいなものだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:52.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここは　もう　ずっと夜だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ　人形がない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:21.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,また隠したのね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:35.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今日も私の勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:49.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:08.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの空の向こうは　どこなんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:17.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここに誰もいないのは　みんな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:22.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの空の向こうに行ってしまったからかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:46.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんな風に　小さな空に星が輝いてるのを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:50.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,前にもどこかで見たことがある気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:04.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　ここは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:11.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何もかもが綺麗で心地よくて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:19.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何かを思い出すのが億劫になる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:36.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ごめんください
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:42.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミはいるか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:45.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,失礼するよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　いねぇのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:59.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,広い家だな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:04.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう時間切れか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:10.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やれやれ　今度はもう少し増やしてみるか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:19.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこ行ったのかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:36.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,みーつけた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　ミズホ　何してるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミと遊んでるの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前まで　まだそんなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,止してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:59.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,母さんはまた妙な輩を呼んでるし
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:03.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いいか　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:06.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミはきっと誰かに攫われちまったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父さんが必ず探し出すから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:11.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もうそういうことはやめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:18.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも私　本当に見たの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:20.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それは夢だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:26.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,井戸の底には　何にもありはしなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ギンコさん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここでしたか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:56.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いかがでした　イズミは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:59.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　時間切れでした
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:07.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　娘さんは確かにここで生きています
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:14.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,互いを捉えられなくなっているだけです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:20.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しかし　一度に同調していられる時間は僅かです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:26.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それ以上続けると　こっちも戻ることを忘れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:30.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あちら側と水の合う者は特にね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:37.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,明日また　同調してみます
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:53.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:56.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,家にいるのね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:02.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　見えんかもしれんがな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:06.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やっぱり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前さん　見えるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:11.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ううん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:15.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　いつも私の人形を誰かが持っていくの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:19.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミはいつもそうしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:21.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,自分の人形　持ってるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:27.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だから今も　人形を隠して　イズミと遊んでるの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:49.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,また　ない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:52.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今日はどこに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:09:59.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,みつけたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ　待て
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,話を聞け
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:11.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前の母親に頼まれて　お前を連れ戻しにきた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:16.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前は　家の裏山の古井戸に落ちて　
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こっち側に来ちまったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何言ってるの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:27.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,井戸なんて知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私の家はここよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:34.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,随分と　こっちの水が合うようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:42.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが　待ってる者のいるところが　お前の帰る場所だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:48.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの空の向こうで　お前を待ってる者がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:53.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,毎日食事を作って待ってる母親　
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:57.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,人形を隠して遊んでる姉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,思い出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:04.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここは　お前のいるべき場所じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:10.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まずい　時間はねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,勝手にやらせてもらうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:43.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何して…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,静かに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:58.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミ　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:01.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,戻っておいで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:15.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ね　ミズホちゃん　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:19.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,井戸の底に星が光ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:23.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:27.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほら　あんなにたくさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何もないじゃない　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねえ　もう家帰ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.82,0:12:38.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここで遊ぶと叱られるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃ　もうおいてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:47.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あー　待ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:06.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミ　人形で遊ぼうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:15.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ　星の数が減ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:21.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ね　私の人形貸してあげるから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:25.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いい　すぐ返せっていうもん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:30.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃ　あんたにあげるから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:32.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:34.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:54.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほら　見える？綺麗でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:05.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　また数が減ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミ　ここにいるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何もない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あったのはこれだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:55.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんなはずない　私見たの　イズミが落ちるとこ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いい加減なことを言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:02.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ミズホ　お前またイズミと喧嘩したんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それでイズミは家を…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:11.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミはどこか他の場所にきっといる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,大丈夫よ　母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私　あのギンコさんの言うことを信じる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:34.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:08.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,井戸から煙が上がったら　井戸の底に向かって呼んでください
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:12.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,よし　まだいるな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これくらいにしとくか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:27.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これからもう一度イズミさんと同調してみます
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:31.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,恐らく記憶を無くしてるはずですが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,取り戻せれば戻ってくることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:38.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,が　時間は限られている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:41.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,間に合わないようなら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:45.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あちら側から無理やり　こちらに繋がりを作ります
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,下準備はしてあります
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:54.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうすれば　ここからイズミさんに声が届くはずです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:07.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミ　イズミ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:13.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ミズホちゃん　お母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:19.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここよ　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:25.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:30.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今の　イズミの声　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:31.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここよって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,家のほうからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰だ　焚火なんか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:56.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:11.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:22.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,星も戻ったようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:28.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　前よりだいぶ少なくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:32.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれは「井星」と言ってな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:41.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「光脉」という生命の元の流れがぶつかる土地の井戸に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,稀に現れる現象だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:49.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ　光脈がぶつかってできる火花みたいなもんか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:55.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そいつに大量に触れると　お前さんのようになっちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:03.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,数が減ってるのは　光脈の位置がずれてきてるのかもしれんな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:15.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何にせよ　お前には与り知れねぇ遠い世のことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう別れを言うんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:25.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:30.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ　もう退きなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:37.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お父さん　私　ここにはもう来ないから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:41.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これ以上心配させないでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お父さん　それ　何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:58.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと井戸の神様が息が苦しくないようにな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,土の底は　　　　　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:31.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,冷たいか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,苦しいか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:35.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,怖いか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:38.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,寂しいか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その底は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:21:02.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,清らかな水の　無数の星の　栖む所
